<div id="pf4b" class="pf w0 hb" data-page-no="4b"><div class="pc pc4b w0 hb"><div class="t m150 xf7 h17 y4b4 ff7 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _54"> </span><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _55"> </span><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m4 x31 h58 y8df ff3 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m6f9 x1c h58 y8df ff3 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m6fa xf3 h21 y41a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">June 5 </div><div class="t m6fa xf7 h17 y328 ff7 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _56"> </span><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span><span class="_ _57"> </span><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m64f x4f h1a y817 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY: Read through Psalm 119 again, comparing its </div><div class="t m19c x4f h1a y819 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">message with that of the book of Romans. Read &quot;The Knowledge </div><div class="t m21f x4f h1a y8e0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Received Through God&apos;s Word&quot; in </div><div class="t m27 x19 h28 y8e0 ff6 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Ministry of Healing, </div><div class="t mbc x7b h1a y8e0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 458-</div><div class="t m65 x4f h1a y81c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">466; &quot;Bible Teaching and Study&quot; in </div><div class="t m2c3 xdc h28 y81c ff6 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Education, </div><div class="t m6fb x62 h1a y81c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 185-192. </div><div class="t m6fc x4f h25 y8e1 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DISCUSSION QUESTIONS: </div><div class="t m18a x0 h1a y119 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t md6 xc9 h1a y119 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When and how did you discover that power to obey God&apos;s </div><div class="t m31d xc9 h1a y8e2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">law does not result from your unaided efforts, but from re-</div><div class="t m427 xc9 h1a y8e3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ceiving Christ&apos;s power by faith? </div><div class="t m18f x0 h1a y8e4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m426 xc9 h1a y8e4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What has obedience to God&apos;s law by faith in Christ done for </div><div class="t md0 xc9 h1a y8e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you personally? What and where would you be today if you </div><div class="t m3fc xc9 h1a y8e6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">had not accepted the will of God as stated in His law? </div><div class="t m361 x33 h25 y8e7 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m19c x42 h1a y8e7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s law, commandments, and statutes are not bur-</div><div class="t m7a x33 h1a y8e8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">densome. The secret is to have them in the heart, which will be a </div><div class="t m67 x33 h1a y8e9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">delight and make it a pleasure to obey them. </div><div class="t m6fd x20 h5a y386 ff5 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Don&apos;t ask that dollar where it went; </div><div class="t m516 x75 h5a y8ea ff5 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Tell it where to go! </div><div class="t m6fe xd h25 y8eb ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">— H. </div><div class="t m6ff x4 h1a y8ec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">D. Singleton </div><div class="t m1a6 xc9 h5b y8ed ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Send your dollars off for this quarter&apos;s Thirteenth </div><div class="t m15c xc9 h5b y8ee ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath projects on the back cover. </div><div class="t m700 x92 h21 y8ef ff5 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Twenty</div><div class="t m6f7 x5c h14 y3b0 ff5 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m701 x31 h21 y3b0 ff5 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">five </div><div class="t m702 xb8 h21 y8f0 ff5 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">percent of the offering will support these projects. </div><div class="t m62c xbb h28 y8f1 ff2 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">75 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
